content:
User: I'm not sure if 'browse' works with download links, as it's designed for HTML pages. The view link likely shows the content in a web page I can parse, so it's probably better.

Grok: If the file is text-based, using 'browse' with the download link might return the raw text. I'll try URL: https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1WKOUjkKCUUBQv7u3hlwPvTLdyTIcf1fm and query "file content" to see if it works.
